                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a3">
                           <locus target="#175va">ff. 175va-176va</locus>
                           <desc><ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3059RepCh339"> salām-hymn for St Mary</ref>.</desc>
                           <q xml:lang="gez"> ሰላም፡ ሰላም፡ ለዝከረ፡
                              ስምኪ፡ በአምኃ፡ ስርከ፡ ወነግሀ፡ ማርያም፡ ደብተራ፡ ለኤዶም፡ በከተማሃ።…</q>
                          
                           <note>. The text is written in the same hand as Additio 4. </note>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a4">
                           <locus target="#176va">ff. 176va-177ra</locus>
                           <desc> Unidentified hymn for St Mary.  </desc>
                           <q xml:lang="gez"> ተከዘ፡ ሥጋ፡ ወነፍስ፡ ከመ፡
                              ኢይምጻእ፡ ኃቤየ። እምንዋየ፡ ክብር፡ አትረብኩ፡ ነፍሰ፡ ዚአየ፡ ባሕርየ። ማርያም፡ ገጸኪ፡ እፈቱ፡
                              ርእየ።…</q>
                           
                           <note> The text is written in the same hand as Additio 3. The name of
                              Näṣṣärä ʾAb has been added, in another secondary hand, into the
